"As a user, I want to be able to edit my post, so I may correct errors"

Whenever a user needs to update their post or make corrects to it there will be an option to change the post. This option will only be avalible to the owner of the post. 

Scenario: User wants to edit post
Given that they are viewing their post
When the user selects the post options button
And selects the edit post option
Then they will be able to change the text on their post
